I don't really know how to introduce this other than.. Hey, I got a new car! Its an Acura TSX (2004), white (well pearl/ivory) exterior and a parchment (tan leather) interior. The story of how I got this car and how I could afford it is a bit long, but suffice it to say that its something to do with my parents thanking me for tuition that I made them not have to pay (thats a mouthful). The pictures here are not that great, but there all I have for now. I'll take some better ones soon.
